Areva, Iberdrola Agree Sea-Based Wind Power Accord, Echos Says

-- B y   D a v i d   W h i t e h o u s e
-- 
2011-06-29T04:19:21Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-29/areva-iberdrola-agree-sea-based-wind-power-accord-echos-says.html
Areva SA and  Iberdrola Renovables SA (IBR) 
have agreed to present a joint offer for French sea-based wind
power generation tenders in the Saint-Brieuc and Saint-Nazaire
zones, daily Les Echos reported, without citing anyone.  The agreement is likely to be announced today, and may soon
be extended to include an unidentified construction company, the
newspaper said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
David Whitehouse at 
 dwhitehouse1@bloomberg.net  